</table>
<p>In this section, the <a href="/wiki/Phonology" title="Phonology">phonology</a> of Khalkha Mongolian will be discussed in sections on Vowels, Consonants, Phonotactics and Stress.</p>
<h4><span class="mw-headline" id="Vowels">Vowels</span></h4>
<dl>
<dd>
<table class="wikitable" style="text-align: center;">
