<th align="left" colspan="2"><a href="/wiki/Approximant_consonant" title="Approximant consonant">Approximant</a></th>
<td align="center"><span title="Representation in the International Phonetic Alphabet (IPA)" class="IPA">w̜</span></td>
<td align="center"><span title="Representation in the International Phonetic Alphabet (IPA)" class="IPA">w̜ʲ</span></td>
